  <prompt>Implement metadata-driven Lookup-field discovery per spec.md FR-1A.1 through FR-1A.4 + FR-1A.7. Queries Dataverse EntityDefinitions API; filters to Lookups whose Targets include configured identity tables; applies global exclusions + per-entity overrides; derives role name via CamelCase strategy; caches per-entity descriptors with 1h TTL.</prompt>
  <goal>Service returns ordered list of MembershipDescriptor for any entity type. Discovery for sprk_matter includes owner, owningteam, owningbusinessunit, sprk_assignedattorney1/2 (Contact), sprk_assignedparalegal1/2 (Contact), sprk_assignedlawfirm1/2 (sprk_organization per Q4), sprk_assignedtointernal, sprk_assignedtoexternal. Excludes createdby/modifiedby/etc.</goal>
  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">AI architecture — service lives under Services/Ai/Membership/</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-009">Redis cache for metadata (1h TTL)</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-010">Inject as concrete; interface allowed (testing seam)</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec Q4">sprk_assignedlawfirm1/2 target = sprk_organization → identityType: Organization</constraint>
    <constraint source="bff-extensions.md §A">BFF pre-merge checklist</constraint>
  </constraints>
  <knowledge>
    <topic>dataverse-metadata-discovery</topic>
    <files>
      <file>docs/adr/ADR-009-redis-caching.md</file>
      <file>docs/adr/ADR-013-ai-architecture.md</file>
